# ğŸ“ˆ QuantBacktest
A simple and modular Python framework for developing and backtesting quantitative trading strategies.

## ğŸš€ Features
- Clean and modular project structure  
- Supports multiple strategies (MA crossover, statistical arbitrage)  
- Custom backtesting engine (signals â†’ orders â†’ PnL)  
- Risk metrics: Sharpe, Sortino, Max Drawdown, Volatility  
- Parameter optimization with grid search  
- Visualizations for equity curve and parameter heatmaps  
- Reproducible config-based workflow  

